data.text:
Indian Bollywood Actress Preity Zinta, left, with boyfriend Industrialist Ness Wadia leave the airport, after arriving in Jodhpur to attend the wedding ceremonies of celebrity newlyweds Actress Elizabeth Hurley and Arun Nayar at the Umaid Bhawan Palace in Jodhpur, India, Thursday, March 8, 2007. The couple were to head to a medieval desert fort Thursday to be serenaded under the stars on the second leg of their opulent Indian wedding tour, Indian media reported. (AP Photo/Mustafa Quraishi)
